    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.96) + (v0 + 0.58 / v1 + 0.65)) - wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.67)))
    v0 = ((0.34 / wp.exp(v2 + 0.57)) * wp.sin(tmp))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.69 / v0 + 0.86)) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.92) - 0.54))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.25 / v0 + 0.35)) + (v0 + 0.62))
    data[tid] = v0
